            Drive growth and engagement on your site with
            Facebook Login and Social Plugins.
        li
          a(href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/guides/mobile/", target="_top").icon.mobile-apps Mobile Apps
          p.
            Integrate with our core experience by building apps
            that operate within Facebook.
        li
          a(href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/guides/canvas/", target="_top").icon.apps-on-facebook Apps on Facebook
          p Let users find and connect to their friends in mobile apps and games.
